data.description: Home Sweet Home!!! Upon arriving at this beautifully built Carothers home, you will set foot on a semi-circular driveway with an immaculately crafted front porch.  This home has a lovely living room, complete with a wood burning fireplace, high-ceilings, and wood-like ceramic tiled flooring! Your kitchen is complete with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and double ovens. Relax in your master retreat, which features not one but two walk-in closets, and a jetted tub.  The owners also made some additional upgrades to the home by erecting a covered patio, along with a concrete slab sitting and relaxation area, located off the master bedroom
